room_title: Escape room "Fortune Teller" by Portland Escape Rooms in Portland
room_address: 10700 SW Beaverton-Hillsdale Hwy, Suite 118 Beaverton OR 97005
room_description: Have you ever wondered how close you are to the spirit world? Here at Madame Neptune’s we bring your fortunes to life, be they good or evil! You and your friends will have 60 minutes to explore Madame Neptune’s Cabin. Working together, navigating the spirit world and breaking the spell may be enough to escape… The Voodoo Curse!
